(666,1,"2017-11-07 02:00:51","2017-11-07 06:00:51","[date]\r\n[inside]\r\n\r\nHey Jake,\r\n\r\nReally excited to hear that you\'re working on a cartoon.\r\n\r\nI\'d love to hear about the project, I animate—my primary focus is rigged 2d stuff, here\'s my [project id=\"reel\" media=\"video\"]animation reel[/project].\r\n\r\nI\'m currently finishing corporate projects, most recently a video for Chicken Soup for the Soul, but my most extensive animation experience was my music / animation project, [a href=\"http://wet.af\"]Dolphinhood[/a]. I made [project id=\"prelude\" media=\"video\"]episodes[/project] and [project id=\"benefits\" media=\"video\"]music videos[/project] for that cartoon, I produce and engineer music too so I have a good touch for animation that incorporates music.\r\n\r\nI\'ve done some conceptual & experimental projects that incorporated loose animation stuff like this Instagram Stories interview series called [project id=\"finding\" media=\"link\"]Hallway Finding[/project] and a 2d 360 music video for one of the Dolphinhood songs, [project id=\"lockedup\" media=\"link\"]Locked Up[/project].\r\n\r\nThe most recent thing I\'ve been [project id=\"characteranimator\" media=\"video\"]learning[/project] is Character Animator, this is how animation projects will populate fast social media stuff like Snapchat and Stories in the near future. \r\n\r\nYou\'ve done a great job of keeping all your projects exciting for a long time so I look forward to seeing what you\'re working on.\r\n\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n[signature]\r\n[links]\r\n[projects]\r\n[data]\r\n","yungjake","","publish","closed","closed","building","20171107yungjake","","","2018-01-03 20:58:12","2018-01-04 00:58:12","",0,"http://gradywoodruff.dev/?post_type=letters&#038;p=666",0,"letters","",0),
(668,1,"2017-11-07 03:07:58","2017-11-07 07:07:58","[date]\n[inside]\n\nHey Jake,\n\nReally excited to hear that you\'re working on a cartoon.\n\nI\'d love to hear about the project, I animate—my primary focus is rigged 2d stuff, here\'s my [project id=\"reel\" media=\"video\"]animation reel[/project].\n\nI\'m currently finishing corporate projects, most recently a video for Chicken Noodle Soup for the Soul, but my most extensive animation experience was my music / animation project, [a href=\"http://wet.af\"]Dolphinhood[/a]. I made [project id=\"prelude\" media=\"video\"]episodes[/project] and [project id=\"benefits\" media=\"video\"]music videos[/project] for that cartoon, I produce and engineer music too so I have a good touch for animation that incorporates music.\n\nI\'ve done some conceptual & experimental projects that incorporated loose animation stuff like this Instagram Stories interview series called [project id=\"finding\" media=\"link\"]Hallway Finding[/project] and a 2d 360 music video for Dolphinhood for one of our songs, [project id=\"lockedup\" media=\"link\"]Locked Up[/project].\n\nThe most recent thing I\'ve been [project id=\"characteranimator\" media=\"video\"]learning[/project] is Character Animator, this is how animation projects will populate fast social media stuff like Snapchat and Stories in the near future. \n\nYou\'ve done a great job of keeping all your projects exciting for a long time so I look forward to seeing what you\'re working on.\n\n\nSincerely,\n[signature]\n[links]\n[projects]\n[data]\n","yungjake","","inherit","closed","closed","","666-autosave-v1","","","2017-11-07 03:07:58","2017-11-07 07:07:58","",666,"http://gradywoodruff.dev/666-autosave-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
