(711,1,"2018-02-28 15:12:50","2018-02-28 19:12:50","[date]\r\n[inside]\r\n\r\nMagnet team,\r\n\r\nI came across your job listing seeking an animator. Your work looks like it spans a wide variety of styles, that\'s really exciting on the animation side. I\'d love to hear more about what you are looking for and what you are aiming to accomplish with a new animator on your team.\r\n\r\nI animate—my primary focus is rigged 2d stuff, here\'s my [project id=\"reel\" media=\"video\"]animation reel[/project].\r\n\r\nI currently live in NYC working freelance on design, code and animation projects. I recently finished some animation for a new YouTube pilot for Chicken Soup for the Soul that has yet to be released, but my most extensive animation experience was my music / animation project, Dolphinhood. I made [project id=\"prelude\" media=\"video\"]episodes[/project] and [project id=\"benefits\" media=\"video\"]music videos[/project] for that cartoon, I produce and engineer music too so I have a good touch for animation that incorporates music.\r\n\r\nI\'ve done some conceptual & experimental projects that incorporated loose animation stuff like this Instagram Stories interview series called [project id=\"finding\" media=\"link\"]Hallway Finding[/project] and a 2d 360 music video for one of the Dolphinhood songs, [project id=\"lockedup\" media=\"link\"]Locked Up[/project].\r\n\r\nAlong with animation, I worked as a producer / project manager at an agency here in NYC called [a href=\"http://sanbornagency.com/\"]Sanborn[/a], so I am very experienced organizing and executing both large, high-budget projects that involve a large number of teams and quick projects that are experimental with small, focused teams. I\'ve also worked extensively as a website designer/developer, so I understand the best modern strategies for incorporating animation into web. Here is my [project id=\"portfolio\" media=\"link\"]design / web portfolio[/project]\r\n\r\nThe most recent thing I\'ve been [project id=\"characteranimator\" media=\"video\"]learning[/project] is Character Animator, this is how animation projects will populate fast social media stuff like Snapchat and Stories in the near future. \r\n\r\nI\'d love to hear about the content you are aiming to produce this year.\r\n\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\n[signature]\r\n[links]\r\n[projects]\r\n[data]","magnet media application","","publish","closed","closed","thinkmakereach","20180228magnet","","","2018-02-28 15:55:22","2018-02-28 19:55:22","",0,"http://gradywoodruff.dev/?post_type=letters&#038;p=711",0,"letters","",0),
